STATE of Iowa, Appellee,
v.
Jonathan Shane WESTON, Appellant. No. 17-1838 Supreme Court of Iowa. Filed April 26, 2019

DECISION WITHOUT PUBLISHED OPINION

A defendant appeals the sentence imposed following his domestic abuse assault causing bodily injury conviction. DECISION OF COURT OF APPEALS AFFIRMED IN PART AND VACATED IN PART; SENTENCE VACATED IN PART AND CASE REMANDED.

DECISION OF COURT OF APPEALS AFFIRMED IN PART. VACATED IN PART. SENTENCE VACATED IN PART. CASE REMANDED.
